data.description:
Don't miss this incredible opportunity! Now is your chance to secure your very own lakefront oasis! This enchanting lakeside residence spans 1,928 square feet and offers three spacious bedrooms, two well-appointed bathrooms, a generously sized living area, and a seamlessly integrated open-concept kitchen.

Nestled within its pristine surroundings, this property showcases its natural beauty with a private beach and a dedicated boat ramp, affording you exclusive access to the waterfront. Plus, its prime location ensures proximity to all essential amenities and attractions. Act now and make this lakeside dream yours!
